footer.coffee: Støt F1 Calendar, giv en kop kaffe.

form.title: Generér kalender
form.description: Vælg først hvilke sessioner du vil tilføje til din kalender:
form.reminderContinued: minutter før hver session i din sæson kalender.
form.nonOptionsSelected: Vælg mindst én session til din kalender.
form.attention: Sprint Shootout Sessions will be included when Sprint is selected. We'll adjust our Calendar options if this Sprint Weekend format remains in 2024.

download.title: Vælg kalender type
download.webcalDescription: Automatisk opdaterende kalender til apps som Outlook og iOS/macOS Kalender.
download.gcalDescription: For at tilføje denne kalender skal du klippe/klistre denne URL ind i din Google Kalender
download.gcalNotificationNotice: Google Kalender honorerer ikke påmindelserne på fjernkalendere. Sessionsnotifikationer kan konfigureres i kalenderens indstillinger, efter at den er blevet tilføjet.
download.icsDescription: Ikke-opdaterende kalender (.ics) til kalendere der ikke kan håndtere opdaterende abonnementer.

subscribe.title: Abonnér
subscribe.description: Modtag en email påmindelse forud for hver løbsweekend.
subscribe.label: Email addresse

notifications.title: Notifications
notifications.description: Subscribe to receive a Push Notification reminder before a session. Return to this form to adjust your subscriptions at anytime.
notifications.statement: We'll never send you advertisments or unsolicited notifications that aren't session reminders.

permissions.prompt: You can opt-in to receive Push Notification reminders before a session starts. Tap the button to allow us to send you notifications, you'll then be able to choose which sessions you want reminders for.
permissions.denied: It looks like you've denied permissions. Reset your permissions via your browser and try again.
